yz&amp;amp;utm_medium=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_campaign=corey-haines" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;Transistor&lt;/a&gt;（我所有的播客都用它）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.coreyhaines.co/ahrefs?utm_source=www.workspaces.xyz&amp;amp;utm_medium=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_campaign=corey-haines" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;Ahrefs&lt;/a&gt;（我最喜欢的SEO/研究工具）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.coreyhaines.co/convertkit?utm_source=www.workspaces.xyz&amp;amp;utm_medium=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_campaign=corey-haines" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;Convertkit&lt;/a&gt;（邮件通讯和自动化）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.getrewardful.com/?via=corey&amp;amp;utm_source=www.workspaces.xyz&amp;amp;utm_medium=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_campaign=corey-haines" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;Rewardful&lt;/a&gt;（联盟营销和推荐平台）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://circle.so/?utm_source=www.workspaces.xyz&amp;amp;utm_medium=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_campaign=corey-haines" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;Circle&lt;/a&gt;（社区平台）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://http//www.riverside.fm/?via=corey&amp;amp;utm_source=www.workspaces.xyz&amp;amp;utm_medium=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_campaign=corey-haines" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;Riverside&lt;/a&gt;（播客录制）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://sparkloop.app/?utm_source=www.workspaces.xyz&amp;amp;utm_medium=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_campaign=corey-haines" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;SparkLoop&lt;/a&gt;（通讯推荐工具）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sparktoro.com/?utm_source=www.workspaces.xyz&amp;amp;utm_medium=newsletter&amp;amp;utm_campaign=corey-haines" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;SparkToro&lt;/a&gt;（受众情报和市场研究）&lt;/p